@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hlouha(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.30
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.sin(v0 + 0.41) / (v0 + 0.76 / v2 + 0.70)))
    v1 = 0.22
    tmp = (0.24 + wp.abs((v1 + 0.49 - tmp + 0.71)))
    v0 = wp.cos(0.84)
    data[tid] = v0
